The '''Intermediate University College''' is a college in [[Amman]], Jordan that was founded in 1978. Situated in the heart of Amman, the college is known for the variety of courses it offers and the in-depth experience its staff enjoy.
Some of the best well-known graduates of this college are: Abu-Shhab, Abu-Aseel, Abu Yasmeen and Abo Khaled, students that influenced the cultural and social life, and added an element of attraction to the college's overall image. Please feel free to add additional account of events that you might have witnessed at this college.
